Name: ms_chanowner
Author: n00bie
Category: MemoServ
Last updated: 2007-08-10T08:36:15+01:00

This module is a re-coded module previously known as [b]ms_coowner[/b] module by Keeper. Using this module Services Admins can send a memo-text to all the channel founders on the network.
====================================================================
Providing commands for Services Admin:

/msg MemoServ CHANOWNER [u]memo-text[/u]
/msg MemoServ HELP CHANOWNER
====================================================================
Original Ideas by Keeper (ms_coowner.c)
This module have no configurable option.

Version 1.0.0 supports Anope 1.7.18
Version 1.0.1 supports Anope 1.7.21
